text: Marc Gisin (born 25 June 1988) is a Swiss alpine skier. He competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. He is the brother of alpine skiers Dominique Gisin and Michelle Gisin. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Swiss male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Switzerland
